---

<Layout
  title="Manglar — Shein, TikTok Shop y TikTok LIVE sin carga operativa"
  description="Manglar opera Shein y TikTok Shop de principio a fin: catálogo, fotos con IA, campañas, descuentos y TikTok LIVE para vender más sin dedicarle horas a la operación."
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --nav-height: 91px;
    }

    #servicios,
    #visuales,
    #ia,
    #proceso,
    #faq,
    #contacto {
      scroll-margin-top: 112px;
    }

    main {
      padding-top: var(--nav-height);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      :root {
        --nav-height: 79px;
      }

      .nav-inner { padding: 18px 20px !important; }
      .nav-links { display: none !important; }
      .nav-cta { padding: 10px 18px !important; font-size: 0.72rem !important; }

      .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; height: auto !important; min-height: 100svh !important; }
      .hero-text { padding: 100px 24px 60px !important; }
      .hero-photo { display: none !important; }
      .hero-h1 { font-size: clamp(3rem, 12vw, 5rem) !important; }

      .section-pad { padding-left: 20px !important; padding-right: 20px !important; }

      .services-section { padding: 80px 20px !important; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
      .catalog-card { grid-column: span 1 !important; }

      .fullwidth-section { height: 520px !important; }
      .fullwidth-text { padding: 40px 20px !important; }
      .problem-pills { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }

      .gallery-section { padding: 80px 20px !important; }
      .gallery-header { flex-direction: column !important; align-items: flex-start !important; gap: 24px !important; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important; }
      .gallery-stagger { margin-top: 0 !important; }

      .ia-section { padding: 80px 20px !important; }
      .ia-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 48px !important; }

      .steps-section { padding: 0 20px 80px !important; }
      .steps-inner { padding-top: 80px !important; }
      .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important; gap: 28px !important; }
      .steps-line { display: none !important; }

      .faq-section { padding: 80px 20px !important; }
      .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }

      .cta-section { padding: 80px 20px !important; }

      .footer-inner { padding: 56px 20px !important; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important; gap: 40px !important; }
      .footer-brand { grid-column: span 2 !important; }
      .footer-bottom-inner { flex-direction: column !important; gap: 16px !important; text-align: center !important; }
      .footer-bottom { padding: 0 20px 32px !important; }

      .floating-whatsapp { bottom: 20px !important; right: 20px !important; left: auto !important; width: 58px !important; height: 58px !important; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
      .footer-brand { grid-column: span 1 !important; }
    }

    .faq-item {
      background: #161616;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .faq-item summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 24px 28px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq-icon {
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .faq-item[open] .faq-icon {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }
  </style>

  <nav style="position:fixed;top:0;width:100%;z-index:50;background:#111111;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
    <div class="nav-inner" style="max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:22px 40px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
      <div class="font-headline" style="font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#fff;">{brand}</div>
      <div class="nav-links" style="display:flex;gap:40px;">
        <a href="#servicios" style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;">Servicios</a>
        <a href="#visuales" style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;">Visuales</a>
        <a href="#proceso" style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;">Cómo funciona</a>
        <a href="#faq" style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contacto" style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;">Contacto</a>
      </div>
      <a
        href={whatsappLink}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="nav-cta"
        style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#25D366,#128C7E);color:#fff;padding:13px 30px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;"
      >
        WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-grid" style="min-height:calc(100vh - var(--nav-height));display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;overflow:visible;">
      <div class="hero-text" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:64px 48px 64px 40px;background:#0e0e0e;position:relative;">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8c95,#e80048);padding:7px 16px;border-radius:9999px;margin-bottom:28px;width:fit-content;">
          <span style="width:6px;height:6px;background:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;"></span>
          <span style="font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;">Operación completa + TikTok LIVE + IA</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-headline hero-h1" style="font-size:clamp(3.35rem,6vw,6.2rem);font-weight:900;line-height:0.92;letter-spacing:-0.04em;margin-bottom:24px;max-width:760px;">
          Impulsa tus ventas<br />
          en <span style="color:#ff8c95;">Shein</span> y<br />
          TikTok Shop.
        </h1>

        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);max-width:530px;margin-bottom:18px;">
          Nos encargamos de tu catálogo, fotos con IA, campañas, descuentos y TikTok LIVE para que tu tienda venda más sin que tú tengas que operar todo el día.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.52);max-width:540px;margin-bottom:32px;">
          Operación estable para tiendas de 10 a 5,000+ productos, con foco en orden, velocidad y optimización continua.
        </p>

        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px;max-width:620px;margin-bottom:32px;">
          {[
            'Gestión integral de tienda y productos.',
            'Imágenes con IA diseñadas para conversión.',
            'Campañas, descuentos y eventos activos.',
            'Ejecución completa de TikTok LIVE.',
          ].map((item) => (
            <div style="padding:14px 16px;border-radius:1rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.55;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.84);">
              {item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a
            href={whatsappLink}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#25D366,#128C7E);color:#fff;padding:18px 36px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;"
          >
            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a href="#servicios" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
            Ver servicios →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-photo" style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#d6d0c8;">
        <img
          src={heroPhoto}
          alt="Modelo editorial"
          style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;filter:grayscale(100%);transition:filter 0.8s ease;"
          onmouseover="this.style.filter='grayscale(0%)'"
          onmouseout="this.style.filter='grayscale(100%)'"
        />
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to right, #0e0e0e 0%, transparent 20%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:32px;background:rgba(14,14,14,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);padding:18px 24px;border-radius:1rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
          <div style="color:#ff8c95;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:2px;">10 a 5,000+</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.65rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">Productos bajo operación</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="servicios" class="services-section section-pad" style="padding:120px 40px;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom:64px;max-width:760px;">
        <h2 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1;">
          Operamos tu tienda.<br />
          <em style="color:#ff8c95;font-style:italic;">Tú ves resultados.</em>
        </h2>
        <p style="margin-top:20px;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.58);max-width:680px;">
          El repo fuente lo dice claro: subir productos, crear fotos, manejar precios, campañas y contenido consume horas. Aquí concentramos esa misma promesa en un sistema visualmente más premium, pero con el mismo enfoque operativo.
        </p>
        <div style="height:3px;width:72px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff8c95,#e80048);border-radius:9999px;margin-top:20px;"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;">
        <div class="catalog-card" style="grid-column:span 2;background:#161616;border-radius:1.5rem;padding:48px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:3rem;color:#ff8c95;margin-bottom:24px;display:block;">{serviceCards[0].icon}</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline" style="font-size:2.25rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:16px;">
            {serviceCards[0].title}
          </h3>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.62);line-height:1.75;max-width:520px;margin-bottom:28px;">
            {serviceCards[0].description}
          </p>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
            {serviceCards[0].items.map((item) => (
              <li style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:0.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.66);">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:1rem;color:#ff8c95;">check_circle</span>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <div style="position:absolute;bottom:-20px;right:-20px;opacity:0.04;">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:200px;color:#ff8c95;">inventory_2</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#161616;border-radius:1.5rem;padding:36px;border:1px solid rgba(255,140,149,0.18);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;">
          <div>
            <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8c95,#e80048);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:24px;">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:24px;color:#fff;">{serviceCards[3].icon}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline" style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:12px;">{serviceCards[3].title}</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.62);">{serviceCards[3].description}</p>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:32px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
            <span style="font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ff8c95;">Canal repetible</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        {serviceCards.slice(1, 3).map((service) => (
          <div style="background:#161616;border-radius:1.5rem;padding:36px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:20px;display:block;color:#ff8c95;">
              {service.icon}
            </span>
            <h3 class="font-headline" style="font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:12px;">{service.title}</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.58);">{service.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}

        <div style="background:#161616;border-radius:1.5rem;padding:36px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:2.5rem;color:#ff8c95;margin-bottom:20px;display:block;">{serviceCards[4].icon}</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline" style="font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:12px;">{serviceCards[4].title}</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.58);">{serviceCards[4].description}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="fullwidth-section" style="position:relative;height:560px;overflow:hidden;">
      <img src={productionPhoto} alt="Producción editorial" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 30%;filter:brightness(0.6);" />
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,#0e0e0e 0%,rgba(14,14,14,0.2) 60%,transparent 100%);"></div>
      <div class="fullwidth-text" style="position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:60px 40px;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:3rem;color:#ff8c95;margin-bottom:16px;display:block;">schedule</span>
        <h3 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;margin-bottom:12px;">
          El tiempo operativo está<br />
          <em style="color:#ff8c95;font-style:italic;">frenando tu crecimiento.</em>
        </h3>
        <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);max-width:640px;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:28px;">
          Subir productos, crear fotos, gestionar precios, campañas y contenido requiere horas. Manglar toma esa carga y la convierte en operación continua.
        </p>
        <div class="problem-pills" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px;max-width:980px;">
          {[
            'Catálogos incompletos',
            'Productos sin fotos o con fotos malas',
            'Campañas perdidas',
            'Ventas que nunca llegaron',
          ].map((item) => (
            <div style="padding:14px 16px;border-radius:1rem;background:rgba(14,14,14,0.72);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);font-size:0.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.76);">
              {item}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="visuales" class="gallery-section" style="padding:120px 40px;background:#0a0a0a;">
      <div style="max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="gallery-header" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-bottom:64px;gap:32px;">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,6vw,5.5rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:0.9;">
              Visuales que<br />
              <em style="color:#ff8c95;font-style:italic;">sí convierten</em>
            </h2>
            <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.58);font-style:italic;margin-top:16px;max-width:520px;line-height:1.65;">
              "Imágenes limpias, consistentes y optimizadas para marketplace. Sin sesiones, sin fotógrafos y sin semanas de espera."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="max-width:340px;padding:18px 22px;border-radius:1rem;background:#121212;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
            <div style="font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ff8c95;margin-bottom:8px;">Desde el repo fuente</div>
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.64);margin:0;">
              Aprovechamos tus fotos si ya funcionan. Si no, generamos nuevas alternativas con IA para elevar consistencia y conversión.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;align-items:start;">
          {photos.map((src, i) => (
            <div class={i % 2 !== 0 ? 'gallery-stagger' : ''} style={`border-radius:1.25rem;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:3/4;${i % 2 !== 0 ? 'margin-top:56px;' : ''}`}>
              <img
                src={src}
                alt={`Visual de catálogo ${i + 1}`}
                style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;filter:grayscale(80%);transition:filter 0.5s ease,transform 0.5s ease;"
                onmouseover="this.style.filter='grayscale(0%)';this.style.transform='scale(1.04)'"
                onmouseout="this.style.filter='grayscale(80%)';this.style.transform='scale(1)'"
              />
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="ia" class="ia-section section-pad" style="padding:120px 40px;">
      <div style="max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="ia-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:96px;align-items:center;">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,4.5vw,4rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:28px;">
              Fotos de producto con<br /><em style="color:#ff8c95;font-style:italic;">Inteligencia Artificial</em>
            </h2>
            <p style="font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.66);margin-bottom:48px;">
              El repo original insiste en esto porque es uno de los cuellos de botella más pesados. Aquí lo traducimos en una sección dedicada para explicar cómo resolvemos velocidad, consistencia y conversión.
            </p>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:28px;">
              {visualFeatures.map((item) => (
                <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;">
                  <div style="width:44px;height:44px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,140,149,0.15),rgba(232,0,72,0.1));border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;border:1px solid rgba(255,140,149,0.2);">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:1.3rem;color:#ff8c95;">{item.icon}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="font-headline" style="font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:6px;">{item.title}</div>
                    <div style="font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">{item.desc}</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
            <div style="background:#161616;border-radius:1.5rem;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:24px;">
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);margin-bottom:6px;">Sin Manglar</div>
                  <div class="font-headline" style="font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;">Producción tradicional</div>
                </div>
                <span style="font-size:1.75rem;">😓</span>
              </div>
              {[
                ['Costo por foto', 'Más alto y variable'],
                ['Tiempo de entrega', 'Días o semanas'],
                ['Flexibilidad', 'Baja'],
                ['Consistencia', 'Irregular'],
              ].map(([label, value]) => (
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);font-size:0.9rem;">
                  <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">{label}</span>
                  <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.56);">{value}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>

            <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#200c10,#161616);border-radius:1.5rem;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(255,140,149,0.25);box-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(232,0,72,0.08);">
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:24px;">
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ff8c95;margin-bottom:6px;">Con Manglar</div>
                  <div class="font-headline" style="font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;">Producción con IA</div>
                </div>
                <span style="font-size:1.75rem;">🤖</span>
              </div>
              {[
                ['Costo por iteración', 'Más eficiente'],
                ['Tiempo de entrega', 'Mucho más rápido'],
                ['Flexibilidad', 'Alta'],
                ['Consistencia', 'Controlada por catálogo'],
              ].map(([label, value]) => (
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,140,149,0.08);font-size:0.9rem;">
                  <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.68);">{label}</span>
                  <span style="font-weight:700;color:#ff8c95;">{value}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="proceso" class="steps-section section-pad" style="padding:0 40px 120px;background:#0a0a0a;">
      <div class="steps-inner" style="max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:120px;">
        <div style="margin-bottom:80px;max-width:760px;">
          <h2 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1;">
            Cómo <em style="color:#ff8c95;font-style:italic;">funciona</em>
          </h2>
          <p style="margin-top:20px;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.62);">
            El flujo nace del repo original: diagnóstico, orden, operación, TikTok LIVE y optimización semanal para convertir mejor sin cargar a tu equipo.
          </p>
          <div style="height:3px;width:72px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff8c95,#e80048);border-radius:9999px;margin-top:20px;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:24px;position:relative;">
          <div class="steps-line" style="position:absolute;top:30px;left:6%;right:6%;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,140,149,0.25),transparent);"></div>
          {steps.map((step) => (
            <div style="text-align:center;position:relative;">
              <div class="font-headline" style="width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8c95,#e80048);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:900;font-size:0.8rem;color:#fff;margin:0 auto 28px;position:relative;z-index:1;">
                {step.n}
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-headline" style="font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:10px;">{step.title}</h3>
              <p style="font-size:0.8rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">{step.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="faq-section section-pad" style="padding:120px 40px;background:#0e0e0e;">
      <div style="max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;">
        <div class="faq-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,0.9fr) minmax(0,1.1fr);gap:40px;align-items:start;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ff8c95;margin-bottom:18px;">FAQ</div>
            <h2 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.6rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:0.96;margin-bottom:18px;">
              Preguntas frecuentes<br />para empezar rápido
            </h2>
            <p style="font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.66);max-width:440px;">
              Sumé esta sección porque el repo sí la trae y pediste no eliminar contenido, sino acercarlo al máximo. La versión de aquí conserva el fondo oscuro y el lenguaje del sitio actual.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
            {faqItems.map((item) => (
              <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                  <span class="font-headline" style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#fff;">
                    {item.question}
                  </span>
                  <span class="faq-icon material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#ff8c95;">add</span>
                </summary>
                <div style="padding:0 28px 24px;">
                  <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);line-height:1.7;font-size:0.92rem;">
                    {item.bullets.map((bullet) => <li>{bullet}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                  {item.note && (
                    <div style="margin-top:18px;padding-left:14px;border-left:3px solid rgba(255,140,149,0.4);font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.68);">
                      {item.note}
                    </div>
                  )}
                </div>
              </details>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contacto" class="cta-section" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff8c95 0%,#e80048 100%);padding:128px 40px;text-align:center;">
      <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;">
        <h2 class="font-headline" style="font-size:clamp(2.5rem,7vw,6rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:#fff;line-height:0.92;margin-bottom:28px;">
          Tu tienda puede vender más<br />sin operar todo el día
